<section class="section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label reveal">About</div>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text reveal">
        <h2 class="section-title">Developer by trade,<br /><em>detail freak</em> by nature.</h2>
        <p>
          I'm a junior full-stack developer currently shipping multilingual web applications at
          <strong>Kapix</strong> in Costa Rica. I care deeply about code that works the same in
          English, Spanish, and Portuguese — and on every device.
        </p>
        <p>
          Before becoming a developer, I honed sharp analytical skills at Amazon for four years.
          That background means I treat production systems with respect and bring a real-world
          "what breaks at scale?" mindset to every project.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-stats reveal">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number" data-target="3">3</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Languages spoken</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number" data-target="4" data-plus="true">4+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Years in tech industry</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number" data-target="10" data-plus="true">10+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Technologies used</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number" data-target="1">1</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Current production role</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
